@startuml seq_19_manage_drafts
title Sequence Diagram: UC-19 Manage Drafts

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Draft Controller" as Controller
participant "Draft Service" as Service
participant "Draft Repo" as DraftRepo
participant "Post Service" as PostService

User -> Frontend: Open Drafts list
Frontend -> Controller: GET /api/drafts
Controller -> Service: Get User Drafts
Service -> DraftRepo: Find drafts by UserID
DraftRepo --> Service: List of Drafts
Service --> Controller: Drafts data
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Display drafts

User -> Frontend: Create/Edit draft & Click Save
Frontend -> Controller: PUT /api/drafts/{id} {draft_data}
Controller -> Service: Save Draft
Service -> DraftRepo: Verify ownership & update
DraftRepo --> Service: Draft updated
Service --> Controller: Success
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Show "Saved" indicator

User -> Frontend: Click "Publish" on a draft
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/drafts/{id}/publish
Controller -> Service: Publish Draft
Service -> DraftRepo: Load Draft content
DraftRepo --> Service: Draft data
Service -> PostService: Create Post from Draft data
PostService --> Service: Post created (postID)
Service -> DraftRepo: Delete Draft record
DraftRepo --> Service: Draft deleted
Service --> Controller: Success (postID)
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Redirect to newly published post
@enduml